data.description: This immaculate 3-bed, 2-bath haven boasts a refreshing pool, perfect for enjoying the sunny days ahead. Indulge in the Florida lifestyle as you step outside to the expansive outdoor area. With over 1200 sq ft of screened outdoor space surrounded by lush landscaping, this residence is an entertainer's paradise! Whether you're lounging by the pool, soaking in the spa, hosting barbecues, or enjoying a quiet evening under the stars, this home offers the perfect blend of indoor and outdoor living. The interior features a thoughtfully designed layout and abundant natural light. The kitchen is equipped with granite countertops, a pantry, and ample counter space. Retreat to the master suite, complete with a private bathroom, walk in closet and serene views of the pool area through private french doors. The guest rooms and pool bath are on the other side of the home providing ease and privacy for visitors. Extra closet space and a 2 car garage allow for plenty of storage space to complete the package. Located in desirable SW Cape near shopping and dining with easy access to Fort Myers and the beaches. It's in flood zone X with a new roof completed in 2/2021 to alleviate insurance concerns.
